### SyncToCoordinates
PUT {{alpacaBase}}/synctocoordinates?ClientID={{cid}}&ClientTransactionID={{txid}}
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

RightAscension=10.234&Declination=-20.123

### SyncToAltAz
PUT {{alpacaBase}}/synctoaltaz?ClientID={{cid}}&ClientTransactionID={{txid}}
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

