### ─── Alpaca response format ────────────────────────────────────
# Every Alpaca response follows this structure:
# {
#   "Value": ...,
#   "ClientTransactionID": 1,
#   "ServerTransactionID": 1,
#   "ErrorNumber": 0,
#   "ErrorMessage": ""
# }
# ErrorNumber 0 = success; non-zero = ASCOM error code.
